Nodes.Comment: You can [weapon-swap] open the Wurm Mounds.
If the pipe is broken, you can glide from this spot to cross the hole, no speed boost needed.
Just run and click all the Traps / Markers along the road and kill mobs next to the road.
Sword or Shield, Rifle is too slow.
Make sure to clear this camp of Centaurs.
One round of Crab catching should be enough (lure them to the Cages and click).

DetachedNodes.Comment: If the pipe is broken, glide towards here.
Go around this way if the cave is blocked.
